metadata.name: Alpha Block Pass #1
metadata.description:
Alpha Block Pass | TLDR

- There are only 69 Alpha Block Passes.

- Each ABP allows you to claim 1 Free Agent and a guaranteed WL allocation for Block Agents.

- Alpha Block Passes will receive 35% of allocated WL spots, thus having higher chances to get whitelisted.

- Each grants access to the Block Cartel, including custom tools, calls, and 1/1 access to the team.
